<br>
&quot;It seems Shey has gone to finish some business she has with Hades. She'll return when she is done. Until then, she gave me this.&quot;<br>
<br>
:She fingers the half pendant at her neck and smiles slightly. She then turns from the hut, looking back at her friends::<br>
<br>
&quot;I believe that I shall go practice in the fields now. If I don't, I fear these wounds in my side will never leave.&quot;<br>
