Now...we should rest.  I must prepare for a trip to Gabby's home town and to see her family for the Solstice.  With this snow, I will need to pack a lot of warm things.  Seems winter is coming early this year.  ::she walks over and hugs everyone::: I shall see you all later.  Herete :::Hipp smiles softly to them and walks out of the healing hut::: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ucallistoblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>CallistoBlade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Goddess</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#993300>(12/21/00 8:05 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ~Sadness sinks in~</span><hr size=1> ::As she is healing one of the amazons she thinks of her wife Gabrielle,and wishes she were there to help,her heart sinks and she slowly stands,seeing that she has helped out as much as she can,she turns and walks out of the hut,heading for herown hut,Hopeing to see her love,to hold her in her arms,to be..once again,happy to be with someone... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=101.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=101.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showPrevMessage?topicID=101.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showNextMessage?topicID=101.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofth